These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
The people have 7 different hobbies: cooking, photography, hiking, reading, filmmaking, board-games, singing
7 different pets are kept: ferret, pony, mouse, hamster, rat, bird, turtle
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the rat is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
14. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
19. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Hobby   | photography | reading         | singing   | cooking | board-games    | filmmaking | hiking |
| Pet         | mouse | rat | ferret | pony | turtle  | bird  | hamster    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

